name: Bro Kwon's Booty
description: Bro Kwon's Booty is a mysterious set of Arbitrum NFTs that were discovered when Bro Kwon's yacht was destroyed and his ill-gotten gains were scattered across Shell World. The collection contains both Crates and Artifacts. Each Crate contains a surprise Artifact. Artifacts can help you earn Shell Points and may have other secret qualities. You can open Crates or activate Artifacts via the Shell Protocol app.
